{"word":"προκαθίζω","slug":"προκαθίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προκαθίζω</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>-κατίζω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to sit down</i> or <i>alight before</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to sit in public, sit in state</i>, <el>ἐς θρόνον</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: —so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to settle before</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to set over</i>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}